OOC: How many CR Chambers does the Neutral base have, anyway?

BIC: Perplex looked at Aerotaur fall.

Perplex: Maybe it would be better for some of us to get in CR Chambers. I
don't need it, but some of us do.

Perplex walks to a table and drops the injured guy he found on it.

Perplex: Technosis, those guys will never bother you again, they are both
dead, relax.

Technosis comes out from under the table.

Technosis: But Deemos is still alive, he'll come back. Thank you for your
help, though.

Perplex nods and starts working on the injured bot he found. Technosis
looked at who it was and gasped. Perplex loked at her.

Perplex: What's wrong?

Technosis: Nothing.

Perplex knew something was wrong, but he continued his work...
